    "body": "### Language server\n\nsumneko_lua\n\n### Requested feature\n\nApparently, the server always requests the above-mentioned method but the client has no handler for it. This causes a warning in the lsp.log:\r\n`[WARN][2022-12-12 10:27:52] .../lua/vim/lsp.lua:1065\t\"server_request: no handler found for\"\t\"workspace/diagnostic/refresh\"\r\n`\r\nI don't really like warnings, so I hope someone who feels the same could solve this.\r\n\r\n(In reality, this warning is duplicated and thrown twice maybe [this](https://gist.github.com/folke/fe5d28423ea5380929c3f7ce674c41d8) solution by @folke can help here.)\n\n### Other clients which have this feature\n\n_No response_",
